data.description: Welcome Home to this Awesome and Peaceful place to live or vacation; it's nestled in the majestic Redwoods of beautiful small town Boulder Creek & Big Basin Wy. It's easy to get to  about 5 minutes Drive to Town, Conveniences, Golf & Country Club. The 2 car garage is below the single level home of 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, 2 fireplaces, laundry & pantry room, new 20 mil water proof Laminate Flooring throughout, updated Kitchen and Bath. New Asphalt Roof, Gutter Guards, and 6 Velux Glass (top-notch) skylights brighten up the house stunningly. The bright and airy living/dining room offers warmth from a wood burning fireplace and fresh air when you open the French doors to a large upper deck to relax or entertain. The inviting patio and lower deck are perfect for BBQ, recreation or any gatherings. Enjoy listening to the gently sounds of running water and natures' beauty surrounding this Charming Home with many pathways through the terraced backyard to sitting areas, take a nap or reading a book on a hammock. Take a short walk to the Forest Springs Community's Pool to cool off in the summer time or hang out at the parks, Loch Lomond Recreation Area or others nearby. Extra storage room or workshop is next to the 2-car-garage. HOA fees include water. Hurry, call me today for a private Tour.
